I have to. He's my best friend. 
我不得不 他是我最好的朋友

177
00:12:53,430 --> 00:12:54,990
And you're seeing him. 
而你在跟他交往

178
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:58,200
Chandler,I like Joey a lot. 
钱德，我很喜欢乔伊

179
00:12:58,440 --> 00:13:02,210
-But with you -No,don't! Don't,see? 
但是跟你… 不，别说了

180
00:13:02,510 --> 00:13:05,310
You're getting me confused. I'm starting to yearn. 
你会把我搞乱 我已经开始渴望了

181
00:13:08,550 --> 00:13:10,110
I'm sorry. 
对不起

182
00:13:10,550 --> 00:13:14,540
If you want to pretend that nothing happened,I can try. 
要是你想假装没事 我可以试试看

183
00:13:15,990 --> 00:13:18,020
I think we have to. 
我们非这么做不可

184
00:13:19,490 --> 00:13:20,620
好

185
00:13:22,260 --> 00:13:24,320
再见 再见

186
00:13:35,140 --> 00:13:37,010
Are you still out there? 
你还在外面吗？

187
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:39,510
没有

188
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:50,650
Electrifying 
振奋人心

189
00:13:53,260 --> 00:13:57,250
Infinite time 
无穷的时间

190
00:13:57,670 --> 00:14:00,830
There's a Starbucks about three blocks down. 
三条街外有一家星巴克

191
00:14:01,370 --> 00:14:05,030
He's so inspired. Just look at him. Look at him go! 
他的灵感好丰富，你们看他

192
00:14:21,090 --> 00:14:24,020
Thank you very much! 
谢谢各位

193
00:14:24,430 --> 00:14:26,420
Hey,aren't you up next? 
接着不是该你？

194
00:14:27,760 --> 00:14:31,060
-I'm not playing tonight. -Why not? 
不，我今天不唱了 为什么？

195
00:14:32,130 --> 00:14:34,260
I can't follow Ross. 
我不能接在罗斯后面

196
00:14:34,970 --> 00:14:38,340
It'd be like those poor bicycle-riding chimps... 
那就像骑脚踏车的猩猩

197
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:40,870
...who had to follow the Beatles. No. 
接在披头四后面一样，天哪

198
00:14:42,780 --> 00:14:44,940
Ross sucks. 
罗斯很烂

199
00:14:46,310 --> 00:14:49,610
The place has emptied because of him. 
他把客人都吓跑了

200
00:14:49,980 --> 00:14:53,750
Oh,my God,he's not even appreciated in his own time. 
天哪，当世甚至没有人欣赏他

201
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:58,160
I'd give anything to not be appreciated in my own time! 
我巴不得能跟他一样寂寞

202
00:15:01,160 --> 00:15:03,790
好，菲比…

203
00:15:04,900 --> 00:15:06,660
You suck too. 
你也很烂

204
00:15:10,470 --> 00:15:13,070
You're awful. 
没错，菲比，你…烂透了

205
00:15:15,980 --> 00:15:17,740
You guys! 
真是的

206
00:15:18,810 --> 00:15:20,640
You suck too! 
你们也很烂

207
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:30,650
Man! I can't believe I locked myself out again! 
天哪 我居然又把自己锁在外面了

208
00:15:31,160 --> 00:15:32,960
Hang on,buddy. 
等一下

209
00:15:37,130 --> 00:15:39,190
Oh,my God! What happened? 
天哪，出了什么事？

210
00:15:39,470 --> 00:15:42,300
-Did you do all this? Why? -I sure did. 
这都是你买的？ 就是我

211
00:15:42,500 --> 00:15:46,170
It made me feel good to do something nice for my friend. 
为什么？ 我喜欢为我的朋友尽一点心

212
00:15:46,370 --> 00:15:47,770
You're amazing. 
你真好

213
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:51,340
No,this is amazing. 
不，这个才叫好

214
00:15:53,850 --> 00:15:56,910
A TV that appears as if from nowhere! 
凭空冒出来的电视

215
00:15:57,550 --> 00:15:59,710
That's the dream! 
这是我的梦想

216
00:15:59,950 --> 00:16:01,620
How did you afford all this? 
你哪来这么多钱？

217
00:16:01,820 --> 00:16:04,880
I'm 29. I mean,who needs a savings account? 
我都29了，还存什么钱？

218
00:16:05,290 --> 00:16:07,820
You're the best friend anyone has ever had. 
你是世界上最棒的朋友

219
00:16:08,630 --> 00:16:10,690
I don't know. 
我可不敢说

220
00:16:10,900 --> 00:16:12,160
No,you are. 
你是

221
00:16:12,370 --> 00:16:14,730
You do this,you give me advice.... 
你买这些东西，还给我忠告

222
00:16:14,970 --> 00:16:18,840
What you said about focusing on one woman? 
对了，你不是要我定下来？

223
00:16:19,070 --> 00:16:20,170
I'll do that. 
我决定照做

224
00:16:20,570 --> 00:16:21,600
With Casey? 
跟凯希？

225
00:16:21,810 --> 00:16:25,180
I'll see how things go with Kathy. She's cool. 
不，我要跟凯西继续，她很酷

226
00:16:25,550 --> 00:16:27,840
-Or Casey. -No,Kathy. 
或者凯希 不，凯西

227
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:30,240
-Could be Casey. -No,Kathy. 
凯希也行 不，凯西

228
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:32,420
Consider Casey. 
考虑一下凯希

229
00:16:33,220 --> 00:16:36,680
I think somebody's got a little crush on Casey. 
看来有人在喜欢凯希喔

230
00:16:36,990 --> 00:16:39,690
I'll fix you two up. What do you think? 
要不要我帮你们牵线？

231
00:16:39,990 --> 00:16:44,260
That all the pieces of my life are falling right into place. 
那我这一生将了无遗撼

232
00:16:52,740 --> 00:16:57,580
You were really great. You were really,really great. 
你好厉害，真的真的好厉害

233
00:16:57,780 --> 00:16:59,040
Thanks. 
谢谢

234
00:17:00,180 --> 00:17:04,810
Monica tells me you don't want to play anymore because of me... 
摩妮卡说你不想再表演了 因为我...

235
00:17:05,020 --> 00:17:07,180
...and,you know,my talent. ...
和我的才华

236
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:09,510
Is that true? 
是真的吗？

237
00:17:11,190 --> 00:17:13,390
Well,kind of,yeah. 
算是吧

238
00:17:13,660 --> 00:17:17,390
I was trying to be really okay and upbeat about it... 
我很想抱持无所谓乐观的态度

239
00:17:17,600 --> 00:17:21,160
...but I just feel so dwarfed by your musical gift. 
但是你的才华令我自惭形秽

240
00:17:23,340 --> 00:17:24,330
See,but.... 
但是…

241
00:17:24,570 --> 00:17:29,340
Pheebs,that is the exact opposite intent of my music. 
菲比，这跟我做音乐的用意 正好相反

242
00:17:29,580 --> 00:17:32,740
You know,my music is meant to inspire. 
我做音乐是想要启发人心

243
00:17:33,010 --> 00:17:34,910
If it bothers you this much... 
要是你这么困扰，那我…

244
00:17:35,180 --> 00:17:38,780
...then I won't play anymore. 
我就不弹了

245
00:17:40,550 --> 00:17:42,680
No,don't do that. 
不，千万不要

246
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:48,090
How could I live if I knew I was depriving the world of your music? 
我怎么能让这个世界 失去你的音乐？

247
00:17:50,930 --> 00:17:53,060
Yeah,okay. 
好吧

248
00:17:57,810 --> 00:18:01,210
-I'd love to,but I have plans on Sunday. -Well,maybe some other time. 
我很想，但我星期天有事 那就改天吧

249
00:18:01,340 --> 00:18:06,440
-Sure. Just give me a call,I'm in the book. -Okay. Thanks a lot. See you. 
好，打电话给我 好，谢了，再见

250
00:18:09,980 --> 00:18:12,980
What are you doing? He is cute,and he's a doctor. 
你在干什么？ 他很帅，又是医生

251
00:18:13,390 --> 00:18:18,050
-How do you know? -Honey,I eavesdrop because I care. 
你怎么知道？ 姐妹，这种事我最留心了

252
00:18:18,290 --> 00:18:21,590
-Well,I have plans on Sunday. -With who? 
我星期天有约 跟谁？

253
00:18:21,730 --> 00:18:24,360
-Me. -Oh,God. 
我自己 天哪

254
00:18:24,530 --> 00:18:27,990
You are the one who told me how important it is to spend time alone. 
是你说独处很重要的

255
00:18:28,140 --> 00:18:31,100
I can't just go out with that guy when I have plans with myself. 
我跟自己有约就不能跟他出去

256
00:18:31,240 --> 00:18:33,330
Wouldn't be fair to me. 
那样对我不公平

257
00:18:33,810 --> 00:18:37,640
So basically you're saying you don't want to cheat on yourself. 
你是说你不想对自己不忠

258
00:18:37,780 --> 00:18:41,150
Well,if you wanna make me sound crazy. 
如果你要把我说成疯子的话

259
00:18:42,150 --> 00:18:45,140
Saw the new furniture. Very nice. 
新家具很棒喔

260
00:18:45,320 --> 00:18:47,480
Joey has the best boyfriend ever! 
乔伊有你这个男朋友真好

261
00:18:50,260 --> 00:18:51,450
I kissed Kathy. 
我吻了凯西

262
00:18:51,690 --> 00:18:53,020
Are you serious? 
真的还假的？

263
00:18:53,260 --> 00:18:55,130
-Does Joey know? -No. 
乔伊知道吗？ 不知道

264
00:18:55,330 --> 00:18:59,100
Is there any way you think he will understand this? 
你们想他有可能谅解吗？

265
00:18:59,870 --> 00:19:03,430
You obviously haven't screwed over your friends. 
你显然没有背叛过朋友

266
00:19:03,640 --> 00:19:05,500
Which we all appreciate. 
我们都很感激

267
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:10,340
If you'd told him how you felt before you kissed her... 
要是你先坦承你的感觉再亲她

268
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:13,110
...knowing Joey,he'd have stepped aside. 
乔伊一定会退让

269
00:19:13,510 --> 00:19:17,310
Don't say that! That's not true,is it? 
别这么说！这不是真的吧？

270
00:19:17,520 --> 00:19:19,110
Yeah,he loves you. 
真的啊 他爱你

271
00:19:19,320 --> 00:19:21,950
Then why didn't you tell me to do that? 
那你们怎么不告诉我？

272
00:19:22,390 --> 00:19:24,550
I said something to Phoebe. 
我跟菲比聊过

273
00:19:24,790 --> 00:19:27,450
And I thought it was a really good idea. 
对，我觉得这是个好主意

274
00:19:27,660 --> 00:19:30,690
-Yeah,I remember. -Oh,my God! 
天哪！

275
00:19:31,330 --> 00:19:33,030
What am I going to do? 
我该怎么办？

276
00:19:33,300 --> 00:19:36,740
-You'll have to tell him. -Why do I have to tell him? 
你得告诉他 为什么我要告诉他？

277
00:19:37,170 --> 00:19:39,660
-Because you do. -Yeah,I know. 
你就是得说 我知道

278
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:47,040
Would it be okay if I wrote a song about this? 
我可以拿这件事写一首歌吗？

279
00:19:50,850 --> 00:19:54,950
I don't know if this is working out. I think.... 
我不知道这样下去行不行 我觉得…

280
00:19:55,090 --> 00:19:58,180
I think I wanna see other people. 
我想见其他人

281
00:19:58,330 --> 00:20:01,230
Wow. Didn't see that coming. 
想不到会这样

282
00:20:01,360 --> 00:20:04,330
It's not that I don't enjoy this. I do. 
不是我不喜欢这样，我喜欢

283
00:20:04,460 --> 00:20:08,460
I just wanna see what else is out there. 
我只是想看看其他可能性

284
00:20:09,800 --> 00:20:12,290
Hey,Guy. What are you doing here? 
嗨，你怎么会来这里？

285
00:20:12,440 --> 00:20:14,740
I work across the street. 
我刚从对街过来

286
00:20:14,910 --> 00:20:18,740
-lt turns out I'm gonna be free Sunday. -I wish you had called me. 
你知道吗？结果我星期天有空 你应该通知我

287
00:20:18,880 --> 00:20:21,680
I just told them I'd work this weekend. 
我刚同意周末进医院

288
00:20:21,820 --> 00:20:23,480
Okay,well,maybe next weekend. 
好吧，那就下个周末

289
00:20:23,620 --> 00:20:25,550
-Definitely. I'll see you. -Okay. 
没问题，到时候见 好

290
00:20:25,950 --> 00:20:30,120
Yeah,you'll be talking to me never,because you're a freak who eats alone. 
我不会再理你了 你是自己吃饭的怪胎

291
00:20:38,070 --> 00:20:40,000
Sambuca margarita? 
茴香玛格丽特？

292
00:20:40,670 --> 00:20:42,190
It that a real thing? 
是真的吗？

293
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:45,570
Well,we only had sambuca,so it is now. 
我们只有茴香酒，所以是

294
00:20:47,070 --> 00:20:50,570
Listen,Joe. I need to I need to talk to you about something. 
听着，乔伊，我有事要说

295
00:20:51,710 --> 00:20:52,870
What's up? 
什么事？

296
00:20:54,280 --> 00:20:55,750
It's about Kathy. 
是凯西的事

297
00:20:58,450 --> 00:21:00,180
I like her. 
我喜欢她

298
00:21:00,620 --> 00:21:02,850
I like her a lot,actually. 
其实是非常喜欢

299
00:21:03,890 --> 00:21:06,260
-You do? -Yeah. 
真的？ 对

300
00:21:06,460 --> 00:21:08,760
Your timing couldn't be better. 
那你的时机正好

301
00:21:09,030 --> 00:21:10,790
She's not my girlfriend anymore. 
她不是我的女朋友了

302
00:21:11,230 --> 00:21:12,220
What? 
什么？

303
00:21:12,700 --> 00:21:16,860
-Yeah,she broke up with me. -When? 
她跟我分手了 什么时候？

304
00:21:17,140 --> 00:21:19,300
Just now,after acting class. 
刚才上完表演课后

305
00:21:19,570 --> 00:21:23,270
I thought she was doing some scene,so I let people watch. 
我以为她在演戏，还让别人看

306
00:21:25,710 --> 00:21:28,740
Man,I am so sorry. Are you okay? 
太可惜了，你还好吗？

307
00:21:28,980 --> 00:21:33,280
I've been better,but I'm all right. So you like her? 
好多了，我没事 你喜欢她？

308
00:21:33,490 --> 00:21:36,080
Yes,but I don't have to. 
对，但我不一定要喜欢她

309
00:21:36,320 --> 00:21:38,950
No,it's okay. 
不，没关系

310
00:21:42,300 --> 00:21:45,420
You know why? Because you came to me first. 
你知道为什么？ 因为你先来告诉我

311
00:21:47,900 --> 00:21:51,060
I thought that would be the best thing to do. 
我觉得这么做最好

312
00:21:52,110 --> 00:21:54,840
You might have your work cut out for you. 
你可能会很辛苦

313
00:21:55,080 --> 00:21:59,980
When I talked to her,I got the feeling she's into some other guy. 
我跟她谈的时候 觉得她在喜欢别人

314
00:22:01,150 --> 00:22:04,980
See,that's actually what I wanted to talk to you about. 
这就是我要跟你谈的事

315
00:22:06,150 --> 00:22:08,990
I think I know who the other guy is. 
我想我知道那个人是谁

316
00:22:09,190 --> 00:22:10,450
Who? 
是谁？

317
00:22:12,190 --> 00:22:13,630
It's me. 
是我

318
00:22:13,860 --> 00:22:15,590
I'm the other guy. 
我就是那个别人

319
00:22:16,300 --> 00:22:17,520
What? 
什么？

320
00:22:18,830 --> 00:22:23,430
When you were late last night,Kathy and I got to talking... 
对，你昨天晚归 凯西和我聊了起来

321
00:22:23,570 --> 00:22:26,300
...and one thing led to another,and.... 
事情演变到后来就…

322
00:22:26,570 --> 00:22:29,010
And what? Did you sleep with her? 
就什么？你跟她上床？

323
00:22:29,210 --> 00:22:33,150
-No,I just kissed her. -What? That's even worse! 
没有，我只是吻了她 什么？那样更糟！

324
00:22:34,080 --> 00:22:36,850
-How is that worse? -It's the same! 
怎么会更糟？ 我不知道，反正都一样

325
00:22:37,980 --> 00:22:41,390
There's nothing I could do. I think I'm in love with her! 
对不起，我也没办法 我爱上她了

326
00:22:41,590 --> 00:22:42,580
Who cares? 那又怎样？

327
00:22:42,890 --> 00:22:45,880
You went behind my back? I'd never do that to you! 
你背着我乱来？ 我绝不会那样对你

328
00:22:46,190 --> 00:22:49,460
I have no excuses. I was totally over the line. 
你说得对，我无话可说 我太过份了

329
00:22:49,660 --> 00:22:54,500
You're so far past the line,that you can't even see the line! 
过份？你根本就过份到 连过份都不算过份

330
00:22:54,740 --> 00:22:57,400
The line is a dot to you! 
只能算正常

331
00:22:58,110 --> 00:23:02,200
Yes,right! And I feel horrible. You have to believe me. 
没错，没错 我很自责，你要相信我

332
00:23:02,540 --> 00:23:06,070
Oh,my God. Is that why you bought all this stuff? 
所以你买了这些东西？

333
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:07,870
You know what? 
你知道吗？

334
00:23:08,180 --> 00:23:10,550
I will not watch your TV. 
我不看你的电视

335
00:23:10,780 --> 00:23:12,620
I won't listen to your stereo. 
我不听你的音响

336
00:23:12,850 --> 00:23:17,120
And there's a loaf in the new bread maker I won't eat. Know why? 
烤面包机里有一个面包我不吃 你知道为什么？

337
00:23:17,360 --> 00:23:21,990
-Probably because -It's all tainted with your betrayal! 
因为… 因为它被你的背叛弄脏了

338
00:23:22,660 --> 00:23:28,330
This apartment is empty to me! I'm not happy about you either. 
今后这间房子对我而言是空的 我对你也很不爽

339
00:23:33,940 --> 00:23:35,910
And just so you know... 
跟你说一声

340
00:23:36,480 --> 00:23:38,740
...I made that bread for you. 
那个面包是为你烤的

341
00:23:52,930 --> 00:23:56,830
Oh,my God! He's lost it. He's totally lost it. 
天哪，他完全不行了

342
00:23:57,530 --> 00:23:59,260
What? 
什么？

343
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:02,460
This cannot get any worse. 
菲比 他的音乐本来就烂到最高点

344
00:24:02,700 --> 00:24:05,800
Rats in the basement are hanging themselves. 
地下室的老鼠都去上吊了

345
00:24:15,220 --> 00:24:17,450
Thank you. Thanks. 
谢谢

346
00:24:21,090 --> 00:24:22,450
I lost it. 
我不行了

347
00:24:24,620 --> 00:24:26,060
I won't play anymore. 
我再也不玩音乐了，

348
00:24:26,330 --> 00:24:29,350

Would you? Can you finish my set? 你愿意… 你可以完成我的作品吗？

349
00:24:30,230 --> 00:24:31,700
After that? Yeah. 
接着上台？可以

350
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:36,200
No,I mean,if I can help. 
我是说我愿意尽力

351
00:24:41,840 --> 00:24:44,210
Yeah,like I could lose it. 
我怎么可能不行了

352
00:24:45,910 --> 00:24:46,900
What? 
